{
  "texts": [
    "The tables in Bornmann and Bauer (2015a) reveal that most HCRs from Germany are located in Bavaria (federal state) and Munich (city).",
    "The results also show that HCRs are regionally concentrated in Germany.",
    "Some other studies have used the HCRs database-similar to Bornmann and Bauer (2015a)-to undertake national empirical analyses focusing on Brazil, China, and South Africa:",
    "Martinez and Sá (2020) took a closer look at HCRs from Brazil.",
    "The study is based on nine HCRs from the 2018 HCRs list."
  ]
}